{"id":635668,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【立此存照】中共实名反习第一人？！华春莹推特/","date":"2020-02-16T14:51:16Z","modified":"2020-02-17T02:50:34Z","title":"【立此存照】中共“实名反习第一人”？！华春莹推特点赞“习近平请你下台”推文","content":"<p>2月14、15日，有媒体陆续报道称中国外交部发言人华春莹启动了个人推特账号 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpokespersonCHN\">@SpokespersonCHN</a> ，这些多官方信源均间接证明了该账号的真实性。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_635669\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ5NsieX0AEQbgJ.jpeg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-635669\" class=\"wp-image-635669\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ5NsieX0AEQbgJ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"618\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-635669\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">该消息已经被删除</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹2-9.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635670\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹2-9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹2-9.png 1194w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹2-9-300x177.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹2-9-1024x605.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹2-9-768x454.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹2-9-1080x639.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹8-2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635679\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹8-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"543\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹8-2.png 1188w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹8-2-300x296.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹8-2-1024x1010.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹8-2-768x758.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹8-2-1080x1065.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹8-2-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>例如环球时报的报道<a href=\"http://finance.sina.com.cn/wm/2020-02-15/doc-iimxyqvz3063505.shtml\"><strong>《华春莹开通推特账号，发布这样一条推文》</strong></a>称：“这是第一个由中国新闻发言人开通的推特账号”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹3-6.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635672\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹3-6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹3-6.png 1414w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹3-6-300x193.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹3-6-1024x660.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹3-6-768x495.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹3-6-1080x697.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>从环球时报发布的推特账号截图看，该账号是一个<strong>2019年10月</strong>注册的账号，ID是<strong>@SpokespersonCHN</strong>，虽然目前该账号并未得到推特官方的加V认证。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-635673\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5.png 1318w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5-300x284.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5-1024x970.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5-768x727.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5-1080x1023.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>华春莹开设推特账号后发布的第一条推文是：</p>\n<blockquote><p>No winter lasts forever, every spring is sure to follow. （没有冬天会永远持续下去，每年春天必到来。）</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">No winter lasts forever, every spring is sure to follow. <a href=\"https://t.co/n8DNvqPm4D\">pic.twitter.com/n8DNvqPm4D</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Hua Chunying 华春莹 (@SpokepersonCHN) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpokepersonCHN/status/1228818169831313408?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 15, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>该账号近期所跟进的消息均是中国外交部长王毅的活动行程。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹7-3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635676\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹7-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"407\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹7-3.png 1194w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹7-3-300x222.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹7-3-1024x758.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹7-3-768x569.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹7-3-1080x800.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>然而，在2月16日，有推特网友却发现，华春莹的推特账号点赞了一条“要求习近平下台”的推文：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ4Id7fU8AAkBhu.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635674\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ4Id7fU8AAkBhu.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"974\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ4Id7fU8AAkBhu.jpeg 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ4Id7fU8AAkBhu-139x300.jpeg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ4Id7fU8AAkBhu-473x1024.jpeg 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635686\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"763\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-16.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-16-197x300.jpg 197w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-16-671x1024.jpg 671w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-16-768x1171.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-16-1007x1536.jpg 1007w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这条推文来自<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tangbaiqiao\">@tangbaiqiao</a> ，由<a href=\"https://twitter.com/beifamg\">@beifamg</a> 所转发并@了华春莹（意味着可以在本人的“通知”中看到）</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">习近平，请你下台，向天下苍生谢罪！ <a href=\"https://t.co/vrCyw5WauQ\">pic.twitter.com/vrCyw5WauQ</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; baiqiao tang 唐柏桥 (@tangbaiqiao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tangbaiqiao/status/1228759861984260097?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 15, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>甚至有推友及时录制了视频备份，证明“点赞不假”：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">录屏为证，有人要倒大霉了（悲 <a href=\"https://t.co/zj32lIDgjV\">pic.twitter.com/zj32lIDgjV</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 乳透社 (@Ruters0615) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ruters0615/status/1228894811379290112?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 16, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Epic moment <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%8D%8E%E6%98%A5%E8%8E%B9?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#华春莹</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/to7IZdfomJ\">pic.twitter.com/to7IZdfomJ</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 樓上的老拖 (@crabrangoonu) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/crabrangoonu/status/1228909171875205120?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 16, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>目前暂不知华春莹的推特账号是否由本人所操作，也不知点赞“反习”是出于“真心但无知”（以为该功能隐藏）还是不熟推特机制的“误操作”。</p>\n<p>截至目前，该<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpokespersonCHN\">账号</a>的所有Like（喜欢）推文已清空：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹6-4.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635675\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹6-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"165\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹6-4.png 1206w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹6-4-300x90.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹6-4-1024x307.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹6-4-768x231.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹6-4-1080x324.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>或许是该消息实在是“过于劲爆”，一些推友的第一反应仍然是“海外人士造谣”，例如不少人将另一高仿账号 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpokepersonCHN\">@SpokepersonCHN</a>  po出，认为这个注册时间<strong>2020年2月 </strong>的账号才是真，而这个<strong>2019年10月</strong> 注册的账号 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpokespersonCHN\">@SpokespersonCHN</a> 为假。</p>\n<p>因为两个账号的简介、头像、注册地完全一致，只是在名称中有一个“s”的差别，不仔细查看难以辨认。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635677\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号1.png 1234w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号1-300x224.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号1-1024x765.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号1-768x574.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号1-1080x807.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号2-9.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635678\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号2-9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号2-9.png 1244w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号2-9-300x233.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号2-9-1024x797.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号2-9-768x598.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/账号2-9-1080x840.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>但对比之前官方媒体的报道截图，可以看出点赞“习近平下台”推文的 @SpokespersonCHN  确实是“真官方认证账号”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ5NsieX0AEQbgJ.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635669\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ5NsieX0AEQbgJ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"561\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ5NsieX0AEQbgJ.jpeg 912w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ5NsieX0AEQbgJ-267x300.jpeg 267w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQ5NsieX0AEQbgJ-768x862.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635673\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"473\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5.png 1318w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5-300x284.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5-1024x970.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5-768x727.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/华春莹4-5-1080x1023.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>华春莹将新账号“第一个点赞”献给“反习”令不少墙内外网友表示震惊，纷纷发表评论或猜测：</p>\n<p><strong>以下为中国数字时代编辑摘自网友评论：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>@wx*****24：外交部发言人，华春莹女士亲自点赞，亲自喜欢。</p>\n<p>@鹏*****头痛：谁看到她推特内容里喜欢的内容了。</p>\n<p>@古*****狐：她明天要被拉清单了。</p>\n<p>@阿*****a：完了 出大事了。</p>\n<p>@A****io：她点赞反动言论怎么说？不查一波？</p>\n<p>@xi******8：这傻逼估计手滑了点错了，第一次玩推特比较傻逼，她的智商高不到哪里去，她哪有胆量敢点习包子。</p>\n<p>@X****iE：估計她习惯了暗箱，对推特的透明度习慣性不了解。</p>\n<p>@sh*****eng：账号肯定是真的，洗不动了，唯一能洗的就是按错了或者被盗号。</p>\n<p>@Ti*****ity：超级重磅！华春莹实名打响倒习第一枪！华春莹通过她在推特的官方账号于2月16日凌晨给反习推特点赞！它成为共产党体制内公开反对习近平的第一人！</p>\n<p>@li****an：有人认为，外交部新闻发言人华春莹注册开通推特，也算是一件“好事”。以后，国保找你麻烦说不能上推特，则可拉出华春莹做一下“挡箭牌”。</p>\n<p>@T*****1176：所以说华大妈这骑墙派也和孔庆东一样后面有人撑腰而要倒戈了？</p>\n<p>@ru*****020：外交部带头造反？也不奇怪，他们知道每天发布的新闻都是假的！</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">你们在担心什么？你们在害怕什么？ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#外交部</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%8D%8E%E6%98%A5%E8%8E%B9?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#华春莹</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/HQRdjNvJyt\">pic.twitter.com/HQRdjNvJyt</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 酸辣土豆丝 (@hongkong2012) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkong2012/status/1228551266575380482?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 15, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38827,38912,38923,38963],"tags":[39800,13222,39799,25837,17827,36099,8604,39798]}